Class DefaultUserProfileService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.optimizely.ab.android.user_profile.DefaultUserProfileService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.optimizely.ab.bucketing.UserProfileService

    public class DefaultUserProfileService
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.optimizely.ab.bucketing.UserProfileService
    Android implementation of UserProfileService

    Makes bucketing sticky. This module is what allows the SDK to know if a user has already been bucketed for an experiment. Once a user is bucketed they will stay bucketed unless the device's storage is cleared. Bucketing information is stored in a simple file.
